711
00:31:41,799 --> 00:31:43,799
[SPEAKER_01] tko sam ja bio kao dijete

712
00:31:43,799 --> 00:31:45,799
[SPEAKER_01] i šta sam s njelo života napravio.

713
00:31:45,799 --> 00:31:47,799
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ono, priput neki blic,

714
00:31:47,799 --> 00:31:49,799
[SPEAKER_00] oznaje da si fugao nešto sve.

715
00:31:49,799 --> 00:31:51,799
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je puno fuga.

716
00:31:51,799 --> 00:31:53,799
[SPEAKER_01] To je pripuno.

717
00:31:53,799 --> 00:31:57,799
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ali ta činjenica čak pripuse s uočistom,

718
00:31:57,799 --> 00:31:59,799
[SPEAKER_00] da staneš i da...

719
00:31:59,799 --> 00:32:01,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, šta sad?

720
00:32:01,799 --> 00:32:05,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se sad ovajezam tu nekim ljudima nešto ispoštovati.

721
00:32:05,799 --> 00:32:07,799
[SPEAKER_01] To je to svijet.

722
00:32:07,799 --> 00:32:09,799
[SPEAKER_01] Sad da je ovaj bok, vidimo se.

723
00:32:09,799 --> 00:32:15,799
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sam, u mene je tad ušao jedan takav strah.

724
00:32:15,799 --> 00:32:17,799
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo strašno.

725
00:32:17,799 --> 00:32:19,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam tu većem ljudom, onda je nispao u menezinom malutu.

726
00:32:19,799 --> 00:32:21,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam spavljeno napljeno na iza.

727
00:32:21,799 --> 00:32:23,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam spavljeno u menezinom malutu.

728
00:32:23,799 --> 00:32:26,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se motao krunicama.

729
00:32:26,799 --> 00:32:28,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam doslovno osjetio kako džavo stoji

730
00:32:28,799 --> 00:32:30,799
[SPEAKER_01] koriju mog kredita.

731
00:32:30,799 --> 00:32:31,799
[SPEAKER_01] Hlad.

732
00:32:31,799 --> 00:32:33,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam osjećao takvu hladnoću.

733
00:32:33,799 --> 00:32:34,799
[SPEAKER_01] Budio se po noći.

734
00:32:34,799 --> 00:32:35,799
[SPEAKER_01] Strah.

735
00:32:35,799 --> 00:32:36,799
[SPEAKER_01] Padio svjetlo.

736
00:32:36,799 --> 00:32:37,799
[SPEAKER_01] To su zvukovi.

737
00:32:37,799 --> 00:32:38,799
[SPEAKER_01] Udarci.

738
00:32:38,799 --> 00:32:42,799
[SPEAKER_01] I ja, sad na nagovore nje,

739
00:32:42,799 --> 00:32:43,799
[SPEAKER_01] kupujem križ,

740
00:32:43,799 --> 00:32:46,799
[SPEAKER_01] pišem od tajstva,

741
00:32:46,799 --> 00:32:48,799
[SPEAKER_01] korijena krunica.

742
00:32:48,799 --> 00:32:51,799
[SPEAKER_01] Bez obzira što ja još ne znam da li to je istina da nije,

743
00:32:51,799 --> 00:32:54,799
[SPEAKER_01] ali ovaj strah je paralizirajuć i ja ne znam,

744
00:32:54,799 --> 00:32:56,799
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne funkcioniram.

745
00:32:56,799 --> 00:32:58,799
[SPEAKER_01] I jednom trenu na mene kaže, Lucian,

746
00:32:58,799 --> 00:33:00,799
[SPEAKER_01] da ili ja, ili to.

747
00:33:00,799 --> 00:33:02,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ili ja, ili to.

748
00:33:02,799 --> 00:33:05,799
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ili ćeš samo u ovaj način života

749
00:33:05,799 --> 00:33:07,799
[SPEAKER_01] ili nastaviti svojim život.

750
00:33:07,799 --> 00:33:10,799
[SPEAKER_01] I ja ne kažem, ok, ostavit ću sve.

751
00:33:10,799 --> 00:33:12,799
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne moram završiti posao,

752
00:33:12,799 --> 00:33:14,799
[SPEAKER_01] kad završim, kad ispoštim ljude,

753
00:33:14,799 --> 00:33:16,799
[SPEAKER_01] ničim sve i odlazim.

754
00:33:16,799 --> 00:33:17,799
[SPEAKER_01] I tako je bilo.

755
00:33:17,799 --> 00:33:19,799
[SPEAKER_01] I, koliko već je kaos.

756
00:33:19,799 --> 00:33:21,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja osnovim gdje svega,

757
00:33:21,799 --> 00:33:23,799
[SPEAKER_01] sam treba opet ići radit.

758
00:33:23,799 --> 00:33:25,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja onaj, bahatiji osvima,

759
00:33:25,799 --> 00:33:26,799
[SPEAKER_01] treba ići radit.

760
00:33:26,799 --> 00:33:27,799
[SPEAKER_01] Pa noći se spava, ono što radi.

761
00:33:27,799 --> 00:33:29,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam konstantno

762
00:33:29,799 --> 00:33:30,799
[SPEAKER_01] ponižavao druge,

763
00:33:30,799 --> 00:33:32,799
[SPEAKER_01] da bi se ja osjećao već, ne znam,

764
00:33:32,799 --> 00:33:33,799
[SPEAKER_01] na kojoj radi noću.

765
00:33:33,799 --> 00:33:34,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ono, kažem, Buraz,

766
00:33:34,799 --> 00:33:35,799
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, su ti rekli,

767
00:33:35,799 --> 00:33:36,799
[SPEAKER_01] a pa noći se spava.

768
00:33:36,799 --> 00:33:38,799
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako pošpredno sa sve.

769
00:33:38,799 --> 00:33:39,799
[SPEAKER_01] I ja dolazim do toga,

770
00:33:39,799 --> 00:33:41,799
[SPEAKER_01] da ja odlazim na zelenu tržnicu,

771
00:33:41,799 --> 00:33:43,799
[SPEAKER_01] pitat da mogu istolarirati

772
00:33:43,799 --> 00:33:44,799
[SPEAKER_01] hladnjači kanjone.

773
00:33:44,799 --> 00:33:45,799
[SPEAKER_01] Možete se znam,

774
00:33:45,799 --> 00:33:46,799
[SPEAKER_01] šta se u meni dešava.

775
00:33:46,799 --> 00:33:48,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja neopoli liki,

776
00:33:48,799 --> 00:33:50,799
[SPEAKER_01] koji sad dolazi tamo

777
00:33:50,799 --> 00:33:52,799
[SPEAKER_01] i ne dobijem taj posao.

778
00:33:52,799 --> 00:33:53,799
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja nemam,

779
00:33:53,799 --> 00:33:55,799
[SPEAKER_01] prodaj motor,

780
00:33:55,799 --> 00:33:56,799
[SPEAKER_01] noci nestaju.

781
00:33:56,799 --> 00:33:58,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ovi me pljuju,

782
00:33:58,799 --> 00:33:59,799
[SPEAKER_01] ovi me ponižavaju,

783
00:33:59,799 --> 00:34:00,799
[SPEAKER_01] crkvi me odbijaju,

784
00:34:00,799 --> 00:34:02,799
[SPEAKER_01] misle da lažem.

785
00:34:02,799 --> 00:34:03,799
[SPEAKER_01] Užasno,

786
00:34:03,799 --> 00:34:04,799
[SPEAKER_01] užasan period.

787
00:34:04,799 --> 00:34:05,799
[SPEAKER_01] Užasno period.

788
00:34:05,799 --> 00:34:07,799
[SPEAKER_01] Lucija je tu bila uz mene,

789
00:34:07,799 --> 00:34:08,800
[SPEAKER_01] ja se vidim,

790
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:09,800
[SPEAKER_01] to je cužištana prošla.

791
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] Kako su to bile urede,

792
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:14,800
[SPEAKER_01] kako je to bilo teško

793
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] s njezanej strane trpiti.

794
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:16,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam,

795
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:18,800
[SPEAKER_01] da ću to ikad moći izmoliti,

796
00:34:18,800 --> 00:34:20,800
[SPEAKER_01] ina će mi da shodim to uspiti

797
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] progradati kroz trste,

798
00:34:21,800 --> 00:34:23,800
[SPEAKER_01] prste pošto,

799
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:25,800
[SPEAKER_01] kažu po istričnom grihu,

800
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] ne snosiš,

801
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,800
[SPEAKER_01] moram da vam govorim za ono

802
00:34:27,800 --> 00:34:28,800
[SPEAKER_01] što si naslijedio.

803
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:30,800
[SPEAKER_01] Po tom grihu naslijeđan,

804
00:34:30,800 --> 00:34:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] jer puno tog u moj život je ušlo,

805
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:34,800
[SPEAKER_01] miram, greh,

806
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:35,800
[SPEAKER_01] duh bludi,

807
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] i svi ostali,

808
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:38,800
[SPEAKER_01] ti duhovi manipulacije,

809
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:39,800
[SPEAKER_01] laži,

810
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:41,800
[SPEAKER_01] sve kroz obiteljsku stavu.

811
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:43,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, za ovom osnovu sam ja odgovorim,

812
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] nisam ja rekao da.

813
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:47,800
[SPEAKER_01] Možda sam potražio pomoć,

814
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:48,800
[SPEAKER_01] znao sam ja sveko zna,

815
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:49,800
[SPEAKER_01] da postoji,

816
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:50,800
[SPEAKER_01] to moramo da znaš,

817
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] samo mojko viš,

818
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:53,800
[SPEAKER_01] koji jako trpe,

819
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:55,800
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek misle da će nekako pričacen doći

820
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:57,800
[SPEAKER_01] do toga da ne trpe.

821
00:34:57,800 --> 00:35:01,800
[SPEAKER_01] I to je prvo sviđanstvo koje se nasvati,

822
00:35:01,800 --> 00:35:02,800
[SPEAKER_01] ono kaže,

823
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] gospodin,

824
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:04,800
[SPEAKER_01] uzmi svoji križi,

825
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:05,800
[SPEAKER_01] križni za vam,

826
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:07,800
[SPEAKER_01] znači to je jedina ranos koja postoji.

827
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:09,800
[SPEAKER_01] moj život je kroz te periodu deset godina,

828
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] 12 godine brođe od tog svijeta,

829
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:17,800
[SPEAKER_01] ušao kao moć sadašnjeg trenutka,

830
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,800
[SPEAKER_01] koji su to lažni.

831
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:23,800
[SPEAKER_01] i ja u tom temutku postajem svjestan,

832
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:24,800
[SPEAKER_01] uprost toga dvijena obraćanja,

833
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] postajem svjestan da sam ja,

834
00:35:26,800 --> 00:35:28,800
[SPEAKER_01] da ja važan,

835
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] da ja si mrdin,

836
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ja ubojica,

837
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:34,800
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ja bludnik,

838
00:35:34,800 --> 00:35:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ja razbojnik,

839
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:38,800
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ja ono najgori,

840
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:40,800
[SPEAKER_01] a za sebi sam smatilo da sam,

841
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:41,800
[SPEAKER_01] nevam, meritunki,

842
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:43,800
[SPEAKER_01] da sam drugima mogu reći ko šta treba,

843
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] i da sam viđer,

844
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:47,800
[SPEAKER_01] prijatelju Tomislava Poleslava,

845
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:49,800
[SPEAKER_01] nagoga glorantina,

846
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:50,800
[SPEAKER_01] mižnici tako ispavno,

847
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:53,800
[SPEAKER_01] jaganči i Boži,

848
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:55,800
[SPEAKER_01] smili se njeni razbojniku.

849
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:58,800
[SPEAKER_01] Dan-danas, iste stvari u meni žive samo ono,

850
00:35:58,800 --> 00:36:01,800
[SPEAKER_01] kada čovjek ide redovito na svijete misle,

851
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] prije Matejlo tristova,

852
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:06,800
[SPEAKER_01] molim redovito koliko može,

853
00:36:06,800 --> 00:36:08,800
[SPEAKER_01] normalno nisam svjetac,

854
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] zna se deset period su hoće,

855
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] ali da sam priskočio na jedinu misli Tomo,

856
00:36:12,800 --> 00:36:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] u 6-7 godina napravljati na prsteljene ruke,

857
00:36:15,800 --> 00:36:16,800
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

858
00:36:16,800 --> 00:36:18,800
[SPEAKER_01] borba,

859
00:36:18,800 --> 00:36:19,800
[SPEAKER_01] borba,

860
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:22,800
[SPEAKER_01] da se radim sad na ovaj put,

861
00:36:22,800 --> 00:36:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] i ta period kada sam od tog tabora

862
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] do perioda stanog susjeta s gospodinom,

863
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:31,800
[SPEAKER_01] u jednom trenutku je Lucija mene rekla

864
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] "jao više ne mogu",

865
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:35,800
[SPEAKER_01] ne šujet sam, bilo užasno u okol,

866
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:37,800
[SPEAKER_01] ali iz nemoće.

867
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:40,800
[SPEAKER_01] Naučio sam i oto se ono modus operativnijet,

868
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:43,800
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavno djeluješ na način na koji si nauči.

869
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:46,800
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki čovjek u svakom trenutku se ponaša onako kako zna.

870
00:36:46,800 --> 00:36:48,800
[SPEAKER_01] I ona mi kaže, jako onako bahet,

871
00:36:48,800 --> 00:36:49,800
[SPEAKER_01] ne kaže,

872
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:51,800
[SPEAKER_01] na na način na način,

873
00:36:51,800 --> 00:36:53,800
[SPEAKER_01] i dolazim doma,

874
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:57,800
[SPEAKER_01] cijelam na svoj krevet,

875
00:36:57,800 --> 00:37:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] i posto je svjesna da ja više nema nikoga.

876
00:37:03,800 --> 00:37:05,800
[SPEAKER_01] ja nemam prijatelja,

877
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:07,800
[SPEAKER_01] sada se druži, oni ga ponižavaju,

878
00:37:07,800 --> 00:37:09,800
[SPEAKER_01] to je da se šest mesece traje,

879
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:11,800
[SPEAKER_01] ja u njih bježem i skrivam se,

880
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] s druži na ovom crkvi mi svi gledaju s povećalom,

881
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] šta ovaj čita, šta ovaj,

882
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:17,800
[SPEAKER_01] tako ružno je bilo užasno teško,

883
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:19,800
[SPEAKER_01] a ja sam jedino uspio preživjeti dana,

884
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] ako sam primio tijelo Kristova.

885
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:23,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se sjećam jednog dana,

886
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:25,800
[SPEAKER_01] čak i šta da nisam znao da je Bog živ,

887
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:27,800
[SPEAKER_01] da je Bog stano živ.

888
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ma da sam ja znao,

889
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:31,800
[SPEAKER_01] hodam s jednom djevojkom do crkve,

890
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] ona mi nešto priča,

891
00:37:33,800 --> 00:37:35,800
[SPEAKER_01] a ja ne znam smisla njavu dao.

892
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:37,800
[SPEAKER_01] Do te granice sam bilo ušel.

893
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:39,800
[SPEAKER_01] Primam tijelo Kristova,

894
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:41,800
[SPEAKER_01] izlazim iz crkve,

895
00:37:41,800 --> 00:37:43,800
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam živ, dišim,

896
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] vidim boje, vidim sve normalno.

897
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:47,800
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, i daj da mogu živiti normalno.

898
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:49,800
[SPEAKER_01] I opet dođem od tijena dana tako,

899
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:51,800
[SPEAKER_01] i onda opet ispoj, ispočetno.

900
00:37:51,800 --> 00:37:53,800
[SPEAKER_01] Da se vratim u sobu,

901
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:55,800
[SPEAKER_01] sedim u toj sobi,

902
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,800
[SPEAKER_01] i ja vidim njegov rešenje

903
00:37:57,800 --> 00:37:59,800
[SPEAKER_01] samobojstva.

904
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,800
[SPEAKER_01] Moj obitelj je divao,

905
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] je moj pokojni djedo,

906
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:05,800
[SPEAKER_01] od mogaca se ubio,

907
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:07,800
[SPEAKER_01] moj stric,

908
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:09,800
[SPEAKER_01] brat od moga,

909
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:11,800
[SPEAKER_01] brate se je bacio pod laktisu,

910
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] i ja budu se bacio pod laktisu,

